Here is the updated System Prompt for the **Logbook Assessment (C4)**. I have removed the requirement for tangible proof/evidence and replaced Dimension 4 with **"Depth of Task Description."** This new dimension ensures that even without photos or links, the AI will strictly evaluate how well the students actually use their words to describe exactly *what* they did during each work session.

